{"tid":2128042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國能源部公布量子網路藍圖，計劃 10 年內打造無法被駭的新網路系統","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T23:34:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f77896fb2d5ef962332271841744388b87684e","tid":2128042,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"美國能源部公布量子網路藍圖，計劃 10 年內打造無法被駭的新網路系統<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/07/27/virtually-unhackable-quantum-internet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F07%2F27%2Fvirtually-unhackable-quantum-internet%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=65c78c0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/07/27/virtually-unhackable-quantum-internet/</a><br />\n<br />\n量子運算能為許多產業帶來革新，其中量子通訊也是許多人期待的一環，近日美國能源部（DOE）公布了一份報告，提出未來發展國家量子網路的藍圖戰略，計劃在未來 10 年推出「幾乎無法被破解」的網路，為全球網路通訊帶來全新時代。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">2018 年 12 月時，美國總統川普簽署《國家量子倡議法案》（National Quantum Initiative Act），計劃在未來 10 年內大力推動美國量子運算研發進展。<br />\n<br />\n基於該項計畫，美國能源部（DOE）近日發表一份報告，表示目前官學研正積極合作，計劃利用量子運算帶來比現行網路架構更安全的傳輸方法，將美國帶入全球量子競賽最前沿。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據了解，今年初能源部阿貢國家實驗室（Argonne National Laboratory）和芝加哥大學科學家運用光纖電纜在郊區建立了一個 83 公里的「量子環路」，是全美最長的量子網路地面通道，團隊的目的是運用量子糾纏或次原子粒子來打造更安全的網路。<br />\n<br />\n能源部表示，量子傳輸的特徵之一，便是訊息在不同地點之間傳遞時難以被「竊聽」，而科學家正計劃利用這點來打造幾乎無法入侵的網路，預計早期採用的可能包含銀行、醫療部門、國安機構和飛機通訊。<br />\n<br />\n「當最後手機也使用量子網路技術時，將對全球每個人的生活產生廣泛影響」。"},{"pid":"89179335673940360405054004f37542e6c0de9c","tid":2128042,"uid":79793,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"中國：派人抄番黎"},{"pid":"4db038af7d979fe51fc3dff306d69aa68db03222","tid":2128042,"uid":522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"89179335673940360405054004f37542e6c0de9c","tid":2128042,"uid":79793,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"中國：派人抄番黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"自煮燃發"},{"pid":"827f2bfbcea6087be5d3d1d89249aae25076e172","tid":2128042,"uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"香港科技輸入被美國封鎖<br />\n<br />\n相信好快會大落後<br />\n<br />\nIT, 創新行業, 應該會雞飛狗走, 搬去星加坡, 倫敦或矽台<br />\n<br />\n可惜港官認為, 無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e3036a151ddd4e377e9895e142e9224485f21a","tid":2128042,"uid":52358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"chiral network<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f10bb9be0b1262de92efbcb7b094de976dddc75","tid":2128042,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89179335673940360405054004f37542e6c0de9c","tid":2128042,"uid":79793,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"中國：派人抄番黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"好似疫苗咁，話咗自己發明咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但打到d解放軍一半發燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a303713b7529d4ccae4dd24aa39a6347d81a93","tid":2128042,"uid":114347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"有冇美股量子通訊概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940eb7f42b22d594145c8c46b12c29f57e4c2c05","tid":2128042,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"建立了一個 83 公里的「量子環路」<br />\n<br />\n量子網絡點解仲要拉線?"},{"pid":"38e134567b344884eaec79ef3a6864d06d861bc5","tid":2128042,"uid":156064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2e3036a151ddd4e377e9895e142e9224485f21a","tid":2128042,"uid":52358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"chiral net